#: ../../typing.rst:2
msgid "Typings"
msgstr "类型定义"

#: of typing.Literal:1
msgid ""
"A string literal type representing programming languages supported by "
"Pygments for syntax highlighting. This type is used to ensure that only "
"valid language identifiers are accepted when specifying the language for "
"code rendering in the ``CodeVideoRenderer`` class. The list includes a "
"wide range of programming languages, markup languages, configuration file"
" formats, and other text-based formats that Pygments can recognize and "
"highlight appropriately."
msgstr ""
"一个字符串字面量类型，表示 Pygments 支持的用于语法高亮的编程语言。"
"该类型用于确保在 ``CodeVideoRenderer`` 类中指定代码渲染语言时，"
"只接受有效的语言标识符。列表包括多种编程语言、标记语言、配置文件格式，"
"以及 Pygments 可以识别并正确高亮的其他基于文本的格式。"

#: of typing.Literal:6
msgid ""
"You can run the following code to get the complete list of supported "
"languages:"
msgstr "您可以运行以下代码获取支持的完整语言列表："

#: of typing.Literal:1
msgid ""
"A string literal type representing formatter styles supported by Pygments"
" for syntax highlighting. This type is used to ensure that only valid "
"formatter styles are accepted when specifying the formatter style for "
"code rendering in the ``CodeVideoRenderer`` class. The list includes a "
"variety of styles that can be applied to the syntax highlighting, ranging"
" from light and dark themes to styles designed for accessibility and "
"specific color schemes."
msgstr ""
"一个字符串字面量类型，表示 Pygments 支持的用于语法高亮的格式化器样式。"
"该类型用于确保在 ``CodeVideoRenderer`` 类中指定代码渲染的格式化器样式时，"
"只接受有效的样式。列表包括多种可应用于语法高亮的样式，"
"涵盖浅色和深色主题，以及专为无障碍和特定配色方案设计的样式。"

#: of typing.Literal:6
msgid ""
"You can run the following code to get the complete list of supported "
"formatter styles:"
msgstr "您可以运行以下代码获取支持的完整格式化器样式列表："

#: of typing.Union:1
msgid "A string or ``os.PathLike`` representing a path to a directory or file."
msgstr "表示目录或文件路径的字符串或 ``os.PathLike``。"
